ns</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:92:"WordPress Francophone : L’Hebdo WordPress n°227 : SupportPress – Sondage – Polémique";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:67:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/QOlL4_ZPklY/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:67:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/QOlL4_ZPklY/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2014-04-29T21:52:34+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"Benoît";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2763:"<div>\n<h3>Une application pour le support : SupportPress</h3>\n<p>Automattic met &agrave; disposition du public une application gratuite de gestion de support, nomm&eacute;e <a href="http://supportpress.com/">SupportPress</a> (en).</p>\n<h3>Une nouvelle communaut&eacute; belge</h3>\n<p>Bienvenue &agrave; la communaut&eacute; WordPress de Namur en Belgique. <a href="http://www.meetup.com/Namur-WordPress-Meetup/">Si vous &ecirc;tes du coin, rejoignez ce groupe</a>.</p>\n<h3>Un th&egrave;me et une extension d&eacute;di&eacute;s &agrave; Twitter</h3>\n<p><a href="http://wptavern.com/tweet-archive-a-free-wordpress-theme-to-match-the-new-twitter-profiles">Ozh a r&eacute;alis&eacute; un th&egrave;me et une extension</a> (en) permettant l&rsquo;archivage de ses Tweets (en). Il vient de remettre&nbsp; l&rsquo;ensemble &agrave; jour suite aux derni&egrave;res retouches du site Twitter.</p>\n<h3>Un sondage pour am&eacute;liorer WordPress</h3>\n<p>Si vous avez quelques instants, r&eacute;pondez &agrave; <a href="http://wordpressdotorg.polldaddy.com/s/wordpress-contributor-experience-poll?p=1">ce sondage concernant votre exp&eacute;rience de WordPress</a> (en).</p>\n<h3>Les CMS c&rsquo;est le mal ?</h3>\n<p>C&rsquo;est ce que semble penser <a href="http://www.cera-interactive.fr/cera-strasbourg/actu-du-web.php?actu=140425-joomla-wordpress-site-web">Lucas K.&nbsp; </a>de Cera Interactive qui tire &agrave; boulets rouges sur les CMS. La r&eacute;ponse d&rsquo;un ind&eacute;pendant ne s&rsquo;est pas faite attendre&hellip;<a href="http://wpformation.com/faut-il-eviter-wordpress-joomla/"> en la personne de Fabrice de WPFormation</a>. Et vous qu&rsquo;en pensez-vous ?<br>\nAjout : <a href="http://www.web-eau.net/blog/entry/la-guerre-du-web-aura-t-elle-lieu">Une autre r&eacute;ponse ici</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=QOlL4_ZPklY:laSY97JiqPg:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=QOlL4_ZPklY:laSY97JiqPg:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=QOlL4_ZPklY:laSY97JiqPg:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=QOlL4_ZPklY:laSY97JiqPg:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=QOlL4_ZPklY:laSY97JiqPg:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=QOlL4_ZPklY:laSY97JiqPg:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></a>\n</div>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/QOlL4_ZPklY" height="1" width="1">\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:43:"L''écho des plugins WordPress : WP Optimize";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:55:"http://www.echodesplugins.li-an.fr/plugins/wp-optimize/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:55:"http://www.echodesplugins.li-an.fr/plugins/wp-optimize/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2014-04-29T15:49:53+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"Li-An";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"x